description:
Dining, Shopping, Strolling, LOVING Historic Commercial Street - ALL SUMMER LONG!
Come enjoy all the things you love about C-Street!
Every Saturday from June 6 to August 29, the street will be alive with activity!
Many restaurants are open for both indoor and outdoor dining and several stores will be offering sidewalk shopping. PLUS, there will be lots of great vendors at the C-Street City Market. 
In addition, starting June 13, there will be a different themes for each Saturday, with prizes and discounts from individual merchants, so check in regularly for updates and details!
